<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA40">
<l>vāyppō vituvoppa maṟṟillai vāneñcē</l>
<l>pōyppōoy vennarakiṟ pūviyēṟ ṟīppāla</l>
<l>pēyttā yuyirkkaḷāyp pāluṇ ṭavaḷuyirai</l>
<l>māyttāṉai vāḻttē vali.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As for an opportunity like this, there will be no other, come heart.</l>
<l>Don’t go [and] incite [and] make [me] enter into hot hell.</l>
<l>Force the praise of him who, drinking the milk as life nectar</l>
<l>of the demon mother with fiery milk, put an end to her life.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
